msgstr "定義ファイルを作成しましょう。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:789
msgid ""
"Customizing any of the Helm chart values is possible via a separate file "
"provided under <literal>helm.charts[].valuesFile</literal>.  Refer to the "
"<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/edge-image-builder/blob/"
"release-1.0/docs/building-images.md#kubernetes\">upstream documentation</"
"link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Helmチャートの値のカスタマイズは、<literal>helm.charts[].valuesFile</literal>"
