#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1244
msgid ""
"This section covers how to upgrade both an EIB (<xref linkend=\"day2-mgmt-"
"cluster-eib-helm-chart-upgrade\"/>) and non-EIB (<xref linkend=\"day2-mgmt-"
"cluster-helm-chart-upgrade\"/>) deployed helm chart."
