#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1311
msgid ""
"<emphasis>For additional information on the Rancher helm chart upgrade, "
"check <link xl:href=\"https://ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/getting-"
"started/installation-and-upgrade/install-upgrade-on-a-kubernetes-cluster/"
