#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1317
msgid ""
"Verify <literal>Metal<superscript>3</superscript></literal> helm release "
"version change:"
msgstr ""
"<literal>Metal<superscript>3</superscript></literal>のHelmリリースバージョン"
