#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1545
msgid ""
"Choose the desired Edge <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-"
"examples/releases\">release</link> tag that you wish to apply the OS "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC update Plans</emphasis> from (referenced below "
