"literal><emphasis role=\"strong\">ターゲット</emphasis>を次のように変更しま"
"す。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1549 l10n/source/edge.xml:1573
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1668 l10n/source/edge.xml:1696
