#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1553
msgid ""
"A <emphasis role=\"strong\">Bundle</emphasis> resource, that ships the "
"needed <literal>OS package update</literal> <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC "
