msgstr "<emphasis role=\"strong\">ベアメタルホストの登録</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2550
msgid ""
"The first step is to enroll the three bare-metal hosts in the management "
"cluster to make them available to be provisioned.  To do that, the following "
"files (<literal>bmh-example-node1.yaml</literal>, <literal>bmh-example-node2."
"yaml</literal> and <literal>bmh-example-node3.yaml</literal>) must be "
"created in the management cluster, to specify the <literal>BMC</literal> "
"credentials to be used and the <literal>BaremetalHost</literal> object to be "
"enrolled in the management cluster."
msgstr ""
"最初の手順では、管理クラスタに3つのベアメタルホストを登録してプロビジョニング"
"できるようにします。そのためには、管理クラスタにファイル<literal>bmh-example-"
"node1.yaml</literal>、<literal>bmh-example-node2.yaml</literal>、および"
"<literal>bmh-example-node3.yaml</literal>を作成して、使用する<literal>BMC</"
"literal>資格情報と、管理クラスタに登録する<literal>BaremetalHost</literal>オ"
"ブジェクトを指定する必要があります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2551
msgid ""
"Only the values between <literal>$\\{…​\\}</literal> have to be replaced with "
"the real values."
msgstr ""
"実際の値に置き換える必要があるのは、<literal>$\\{…​\\}</literal>の中の値だけで"
"す。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2552
msgid ""
"We will walk you through the process for only one host. The same steps apply "
"to the other two nodes."
msgstr ""
"1つのホストのプロセスについてのみ説明します。他の2つのノードにも同じ手順が適"
"用されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2553
msgid "Where:"
msgstr "各項目の内容は次のとおりです。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2554
msgid ""
"<literal>${BMC_NODE1_USERNAME}</literal> — The username for the BMC of the "
"first bare-metal host."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${BMC_NODE1_USERNAME}</literal> — 最初のベアメタルホストのBMCのユー"
"ザ名。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2555
msgid ""
"<literal>${BMC_NODE1_PASSWORD}</literal> — The password for the BMC of the "
"first bare-metal host."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${BMC_NODE1_PASSWORD}</literal> — 最初のベアメタルホストのBMCのパス"
"ワード。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2556
msgid ""
"<literal>${BMC_NODE1_MAC}</literal> — The MAC address of the first bare-"
"metal host to be used."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${BMC_NODE1_MAC}</literal> — 使用する最初のベアメタルホストのMACアド"
"レス。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2557
msgid ""
"<literal>${BMC_NODE1_ADDRESS}</literal> — The URL for the first bare-metal "
"host BMC (for example, <literal>redfish-virtualmedia://192.168.200.75/"
"redfish/v1/Systems/1/</literal>). To learn more about the different options "
"available depending on your hardware provider, check the following <link xl:"
"href=\"https://github.com/metal3-io/baremetal-operator/blob/main/docs/api.md"
"\">link</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${BMC_NODE1_ADDRESS}</literal> — 最初のベアメタルホストのBMCのURL "
"(例: <literal>redfish-virtualmedia://192.168.200.75/redfish/v1/Systems/1/</"
"literal>)。ハードウェアプロバイダに応じて使用できる各種のオプションの詳細につ"
"いては、<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/metal3-io/baremetal-operator/blob/"
"main/docs/api.md\">こちらのリンク</link>を確認してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2558
