#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2746
msgid ""
"Summary: SUSE Edge 3.0.2 is the second z-stream release in the SUSE Edge 3.0 "
"portfolio."
msgstr ""
"概要: SUSE Edge 3.0.2は、SUSE Edge 3.0ポートフォリオの2番目のzストリームリ"
"リースです。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2747 l10n/source/edge.xml:2840
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2935
msgid "New Features"
msgstr "新機能"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2748
msgid ""
"The Metal<superscript>3</superscript> chart now supports static network "
"configuration without any <literal>mac-address</literal>: <link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/suse-edge/charts/pull/134\">SUSE Edge issue #134</link>"
msgstr ""
"Metal<superscript>3</superscript>チャートは、<literal>mac-address</literal>な"
"しで静的ネットワークをサポートするようになりました: <link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/suse-edge/charts/pull/134\">SUSE Edge issue #134</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2749
msgid ""
"KubeVirt is updated from <literal>1.1.1</literal> to <literal>1.2.2</"
"literal> for details of new features refer to the: <link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/kubevirt/kubevirt/releases\">Upstream Release Notes</link>"
msgstr ""
"KubeVirtは、 <literal>1.1.1</literal>から<literal>1.2.2</literal>に更新されま"
"した。新機能の詳細については、 <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/kubevirt/"
"kubevirt/releases\">アップストリームリリースノート</link>を参照してください"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2750 l10n/source/edge.xml:2846
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2937
msgid "Bug &amp; Security Fixes"
msgstr "バグおよびセキュリティの修正"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2751
msgid ""
"The Metal<superscript>3</superscript> chart fixes an issue where host "
"reprovisioning may use stale static network configuration: <link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/suse-edge/charts/pull/133\">SUSE Edge issue #133</link>"
msgstr ""
"Metal<superscript>3</superscript>チャートは、ホストの再ビジョニングで古い静的"
"ネットワーク設定が使用される場合がある問題を修正しています: <link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/suse-edge/charts/pull/133\">SUSE Edgeの問題#133</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2752
msgid ""
"The RKE2 Cluster API provider fixes an issue when specifying TLS "
"configuration for a local registry: <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/"
"rancher/cluster-api-provider-rke2/pull/357\">RKE2 Provider issue #357</link>"
msgstr ""
"RKE2 Cluster APIプロバイダは、ローカルレジストリのTLS設定を指定する際の問題を"
"修正しています: <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/cluster-api-"
"provider-rke2/pull/357\">RKE2プロバイダの問題#357</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2753
msgid ""
"The RKE2 Cluster API provider fixes an issue causing rke2-install to error "
"after system reboot: <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/cluster-api-"
"provider-rke2/pull/346\">RKE2 Provider issue #346</link>"
msgstr ""
"RKE2 Cluster APIプロバイダは、システムの再起動後にrke2-installがエラーになる"
"問題を修正しています: <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/cluster-api-"
"provider-rke2/pull/346\">RKE2プロバイダの問題#346</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2754
msgid ""
"KubeVirt is updated to include several security fixes: <link xl:href="
"\"https://www.suse.com/support/update/announcement/2024/suse-"
"su-20242669-1\">Kubevirt Update</link>"
msgstr ""
"KuKubeVirtはいくつかのセキュリティ修正を含むように更新されています: <link xl:"
"href=\"https://www.suse.com/support/update/announcement/2024/suse-"
"su-20242669-1\">Kubevirtの更新</link>"

